# Trivy ignore file for Code Engine image scan.
# These CVEs are in transitive dependencies we cannot directly control.

# jackson-core inside ray_dist.jar (bundled in ray pip package).
# Cannot upgrade without a new ray release. Low risk: JAR is not
# directly exposed — ray is a transitive dep of qiskit-serverless.
GHSA-72hv-8253-57qq

# mathjax <3.2.1 — prototype pollution via crafted MathML input.
# Bundled inside jupyter_server/nbconvert; cannot upgrade independently.
CVE-2023-39663

# underscore.js <1.12.1 — arbitrary code execution via template function.
# Bundled inside jupyter_server/nbclassic; cannot upgrade independently.
CVE-2026-27601

# gpgv (Debian OS package) — signature verification bypass.
# Transitive OS-level dep from base image; no direct control.
CVE-2025-68973
